# Input

```html
<span>really long content that should make the inline element break across multiple lines</span><!-- trailing --><span>next inline sibling</span>

```


# Formatted

```html
<span
	>really long content that should make the inline element break across multiple
	lines</span
><!-- trailing --><span>next inline sibling</span>

```
